I had my 6 Volt 40 hp 65 for 7 years and I hauled literally tons of house
debris from my rebuild job and I loved it. I was never in a position to do the
real body work and rust repair it really needed being only an engine guy and
building a house at the time, so when I sold it and bought my 71 westy at the
time it was never the same. I swore that if I ever found another serviceable
truck I would buy it, and so I have!

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3
71 Trike 1776cc Dual T-4 34 PDSIT-3
